content: For the next 6 months, our analyses lesson will begin at 2pm, instead of 1.30 pm.
We will do necessary changes in the webpage of Analyses Department as well.
Today's lesson topic is a game between Soos鮮v Ants and Savrasovqa Julia

pantrike, Intotherenju, weigui, luwenzhe, alcore, cisco, tianxia, fallnavy, imaccn, shuwang, yyfcsd, bawangwan, moocheng, yzhnie, jamphen, mayhem, pengyu, mumax, whte, Renjufans, sosei, lingdodo, ouyang, coco_yuang.
It was played in year 2001, in Russian First League
By the way, speaking of Ants, it reminds me
that I have spoken to both Ants and Kawamura (ex-world champion), and they both agreed to teach the VIP lesson for you at some time in future.
This is the typical opening of d3. Ants is playing with blacks here.
This variant has been quite popular since 1997.
I remember I lose a game in WC as black in 1999.
And the 11 moves were repeating that path.
But Savrasova chose another plan this time.
Actually, this 12th move is considered weaker.
And most top players have developed very strong attacking ideas for black here.
but white has better choice of 24
so this development of black seems not very good
yy has shown two good possibilities to develop well
Do you want to try some ideas?
no need to worry, even if fail, its just a practice
you just try black stones, i put whites
good guests, and how about students?
how many of you are able to make sure this absence of vcf without using any analysing board?
you are over 1 dan for sure, if you can make it all sure by looking only.
those who cannot make sure, are less than 1 dan maybe
We realized that 18 must be played below
是不是安度不会这个啊？
I am sorry. I will behave.
we are just trying ideas here,
your idea is very good too!
Who else would like to try?
Well, then lets see how Ants played here.
In some ways, this move is better than k10.
make good use of forbidden trap
It all depends on your following plan.
In case of this plan here,
it is not necessary to have k10 at all.
It is practically the same position,
however, here black has a bit bigger variety of moves
In some cases the attack goes to upper side,
and there are situations where black needs a L10 point
or, at least its important that there is no white at L10 that would bother blacks somewhere.
And lastly, black can always use k10 anytime later,
and return to what we have seen already
actually , black has enough time to play at k10 later
That is exactly Ants' thinking too.
Savrasova, realizing it too, tried to make some use of it for whites.
That is, if white could change the 14th move.
She knew that 14-g6 would lead to the standard position with black's better advantage thanks to unplayed k10
So, she changed the 14th move, hoping to confuse her opponent.
Do you think its good or bad move?
maybe it also lost,but better than other choice
Indeed, move 14 cuts off all black attacks on left side, but on the other hand, a terrible g6 attack was left open.
And it is far more scary than whatever comes after 14-g6.
It is hard to defend here already.
because white has nothing at all
other can see but wont say :)
double threaten and stop thinking any more
black can afford many ways of winning here
Did you see by looking only, or used analyse board?
lingdodo and yy are very active today
meanwhile, others can warm up fingers

leto, fallnavy, pantrike, Red_Zombie, luwenzhe, Intotherenju, weigui, shuwang, Chaos, yyfcsd, jamphen, mayhem, tianxia, alcore, lingdodo, ouyang, mumax, pengyu, bawangwan, Ikon, imaccn, whte, yzhnie, sosei, xiaoxuan, coco_yuang.
ok, let someone else try then
So, what can we say about this 14th move? :)
And I am not sure exactly where Ants would have played,
These are the two main variants
do you think black can win here?
it seems, black has lots of opportunities after this 12th move.
That is why this 12 is rarely played nowadays.
And although there are lots of unsolved issues here as well,
and if failed, then maybe black is good
and with another 12th was vice versa.
I think mumax ideas were nice too
So, today's game was a nice review of this 5th move in d3 opening.
Maybe, when Ants will come to teach us,
he can share more of his experience with us
and we will know about his thinking more.
And now, we will end the lesson.
Some of you were so active,
and some did not speak even one word during whole lesson.
I hope, next time everybody is active.
Just like yy, lingdodo, lu and some others.
